This paper deals with approximation algorithms and integrality gaps for a combinatorial optimization problem related to resource allocation. This problem is of interest to researchers in game theory (cs.GT), as well as those working in algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), discrete mathematics (cs.DM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and computational complexity (cs.CC).
